4. **Web Searching Skills**: Essential for locating primary documents, news articles, books written by experts covering aspects similar enough so they can be cross-referenced against known truths thus confirming details regarding secondary claims made across internet platforms where lesser-known but still pertinent stories may reside unverified yet accessible online now-a-days via digital archives maintained by institutions dedicated preserving historical records etc..

